---
import TextH3 from '../components/text/text-h3.astro'
import TextParagraph from '../components/text/text-paragraph.astro'
import Layout from '../layout/layout.astro'
const title = 'About | Guilherme Lopes'
const description = 'A little section to detail who am I and what I really like'
const canonical = 'https://guimox.dev/about'
const current = 'about'
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical} current={current}>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
    <div class="mt-4">
      <TextH3 bold>About me</TextH3>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
      <TextParagraph>
        I'm a software developer who loves experimenting and learning new things. Whether it's building frontend
        apps with frameworks like React or Angular, managing backend systems with Java or Spring Boot, or diving
        into side projects with Golang (a personal favorite), I'm always looking for opportunities to create and
        improve. I enjoy trying a bit of everything—designing user-friendly interfaces, optimizing backend logic,
        or even exploring how to make infrastructure work better.
      </TextParagraph>
      <TextParagraph>
        One thing I really focus on is simplicity. I like to lower the barriers to getting started and keeping
        things running smoothly, which is why I almost always use Docker to containerize my projects and ensure
        they're easy to deploy and maintain. I've also gained experience working with infrastructure, experimenting
        with CI/CD pipelines, GitHub Actions, and setting up VPS environments to streamline workflows and
        deployments.
      </TextParagraph>
      <TextParagraph>
        For me, it's all about turning ideas into something practical and sustainable while keeping the process
        fun. I'm always up for learning, building, and seeing how a small experiment can grow into something great.
      </TextParagraph>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
